graph TB
    subgraph Operator["llama-stack-k8s-operator"]
        direction TB
        Controller["Reconciler<br/>(controller-runtime)"]
        Kustomizer["Kustomize Pipeline<br/>(manifest rendering)"]
        Webhook["Validating Webhook<br/>(vogxserver.kb.io)"]
        CAManager["CA Bundle Manager<br/>(PEM/X.509 validation)"]
        FeatureFlags["Feature Flags<br/>(enableNetworkPolicy)"]
        UpgradeCleanup["Upgrade Cleanup<br/>(legacy RBAC removal)"]

        Controller -->|renders manifests| Kustomizer
        Controller -->|validates certs| CAManager
        Controller -->|checks flags| FeatureFlags
        Controller -->|on startup| UpgradeCleanup
    end

    subgraph KustomizePlugins["Kustomize Plugin Pipeline"]
        direction LR
        P1["1. Name Prefixer"]
        P2["2. Namespace Setter"]
        P3["3. Field Mutator"]
        P4["4. NetworkPolicy Transformer"]
        P1 --> P2 --> P3 --> P4
    end

    Kustomizer -->|executes| KustomizePlugins

    User["Data Scientist / Admin"] -->|creates/updates| CR["LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>(llamastack.io/v1alpha1)"]
    CR -->|watched by| Controller

    subgraph ManagedResources["Managed Per-Instance Resources"]
        Deploy["Deployment"]
        Svc["Service<br/>8321/TCP"]
        SA["ServiceAccount"]
        PVC["PersistentVolumeClaim"]
        NP["NetworkPolicy"]
        PDB["PodDisruptionBudget"]
        HPA["HorizontalPodAutoscaler"]
        RB["RoleBinding<br/>(anyuid SCC)"]
        Ing["Ingress<br/>(optional)"]
        CMBundle["CA Bundle ConfigMap"]
    end

    Controller -->|creates/updates| ManagedResources

    subgraph ManagedPods["Llama Stack Server"]
        LlamaStack["Llama Stack Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP"]
    end

    Deploy -->|manages| LlamaStack
    Controller -->|probes /v1/health<br/>/v1/providers<br/>/v1/version| LlamaStack

    K8sAPI["Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"] -->|CR events| Controller
    Controller -->|CRUD resources| K8sAPI

    ODHBundle["odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>ConfigMap"] -.->|auto-detected| CAManager
    UserBundle["User CA Bundle<br/>ConfigMap"] -.->|referenced| CAManager
    CAManager -->|creates| CMBundle

    Webhook -->|validates| CR

    %% Health/Metrics
    Prometheus["Prometheus"] -.->|scrapes 8443/TCP| Controller

    %% Styling
    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Kustomizer fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style CAManager fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style FeatureFlags fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
